Package domain

Class Complex

java.lang.Object
domain.Complex
public class Complex extends Object

Class:
Complex.

Description:
The Complex class represents a complex number with real and imaginary parts. It provides methods to set and get the real and imaginary parts, and a method to generate a string representation of the complex number.

Control change:

  • 0.1.0: Create class.
